    COUNT(CASE WHEN p.hospitaldischargetime IS NOT NULL AND 
                    (julianday(p.hospitaldischargetime) - julianday(p.hospitaladmittime)) / 365.25 >= 3 
              THEN 1 END) * 100.0 / COUNT(*) as three_year_survival_rate
FROM patient p
WHERE p.patientunitstayid IN (
    SELECT DISTINCT d.patientunitstayid
    FROM diagnosis d
    JOIN medication m ON d.patientunitstayid = m.patientunitstayid
    WHERE d.diagnosisname LIKE '%hypernatremia%' 
      AND d.diagnosisname LIKE '%sodium%'
      AND m.drugname LIKE '%zofran%'
      AND m.drugstarttime > d.diagnosistime
);

SELECT 
    d.diagnosisname,
    COUNT(*) as total_patients,
    SUM(CASE WHEN p.hospitaldischargestatus = 'expired' 
             OR (p.hospitaldischargetime IS NOT NULL 
                 AND p.hospitaldischargetime <= datetime(p.hospitaladmittime, '+1 year')
                 AND p.hospitaldischargestatus = 'expired')
        THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as deaths_within_one_year,
    ROUND(
        100.0 * SUM(CASE WHEN p.hospitaldischargestatus = 'expired' 
                          OR (p.hospitaldischargetime IS NOT NULL 
                              AND p.hospitaldischargetime <= datetime(p.hospitaladmittime, '+1 year')
                              AND p.hospitaldischargestatus = 'expired')
                     THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) / COUNT(*), 2
    ) as mortality_rate_percent
FROM diagnosis d
JOIN patient p ON d.patientunitstayid = p.patientunitstayid
GROUP BY d.diagnosisname
HAVING COUNT(*) >= 10
ORDER BY mortality_rate_percent DESC, total_patients DESC
LIMIT 5;

join medication m2 on m1.patientunitstayid = m2.patientunitstayid
where m1.drugname like '%famotidine%' 
  and m1.dosage like '%20 mg%'
  and m1.routeadmin = 'po'
  and extract(year from m1.drugstarttime) = 2103
  and m2.drugname != m1.drugname
  and m2.drugstarttime between (m1.drugstarttime - interval '2 months') and m1.drugstarttime
group by m2.drugname
order by frequency desc
limit 4;
